details.name: Enchant Totem
details.description: Empowers Earthshaker's totem, causing it to deal extra damage on the next attack. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Enchant Totem becomes a 900 range ground target ability, causing Earthshaker to jump in the air and land at the target spot, casting Enchant Totem there.  Self-casting the ability will behave in the original form, without jumping.
